                  "answerKey": "answer_1",
                  "content": "Drug addicts took over many of the city’s abandoned buildings, causing most of the city’s residents to move to other cities."
                },
                {
                  "answerKey": "answer_2",
                  "content": "Many of the city’s residents who are mentally ill refused to take their medication and so could not function according to the conventional norms of society."
                },
                {
                  "answerKey": "answer_3",
